{"ID":"20260605142237-tabjurv","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260605142237-tabjurv","title":"2023年全国乙卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260605142339"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605142252-nux8xoi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142252-nux8xoi","updated":"20260605142252"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"破阵子"}]},{"ID":"20260605142252-ekffu0s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142252-ekffu0s","updated":"20260605142252"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陆游"}]},{"ID":"20260605142252-rznxl7w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142252-rznxl7w","updated":"20260605142252"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"看破空花尘世，放轻昨梦浮名，蜡屐登山真率饮，筇杖穿林自在行，身闲心太平。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142252-gj5fm58","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142252-gj5fm58","updated":"20260605142252"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"料峭余寒犹力，廉纤细雨初晴。苔纸闲题溪上句，菱唱遥闻烟外声。与君同醉醒。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142237-22xqdt0","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605142237-22xqdt0","updated":"20260605142305"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260605142305-gjsxx2v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142305-gjsxx2v","updated":"20260605142305"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14．下列对这首词的理解和赏析，不正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605142305-yfnw2ma","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142305-yfnw2ma","updated":"20260605142305"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．词人以“空花”“昨梦”喻指过往的虚无，“看破”“放轻”宣示自己告别过去。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142305-uin4n01","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142305-uin4n01","updated":"20260605142305"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．词人着屐拄杖、登山穿林，一个远离尘世、悠游自在的山野隐逸形象跃然纸上。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142305-boh4b7y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142305-boh4b7y","updated":"20260605142305"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．细雨初晴的春日，依然会使人感觉到寒冷，但这并没有影响词人的轻松自得。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142305-5jykhgb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142305-5jykhgb","updated":"20260605142305"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．词人在最后表示，希望远方友人能与自己同饮共醉，表达了真挚的思念之情。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142305-dw7ukff","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142305-dw7ukff","updated":"20260605142305"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．这首词是如何表现人闲适心情的？请结合作品简要分析。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142237-ttjvj57","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605142237-ttjvj57","updated":"20260605142324"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260605142324-gkh1dd8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142324-gkh1dd8","updated":"20260605142324"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14．D    15．①看破虚幻的世界，放弃过往的无谓名利。体现出作者处世豁达的人生态度，旷达自然，超凡脱俗。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142324-h0gsvhk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142324-h0gsvhk","updated":"20260605142324"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"②穿着蜡屐登山率真地饮酒，带上筇杖自在地行走，身体自由，心灵宁静。体现出作者宁静从容的心境，诠释着作者退居后乐观淡泊的精神追求。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142324-mqz6vc0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142324-mqz6vc0","updated":"20260605142324"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"③闲暇之时在溪边题诗，听着远处传来烟霭外采菱人的歌声。写作者对官场失望之后徜徉在山水之间，不问世事，抒写闲适情趣，力求解脱之道的旷达胸怀。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142237-ti3rjp0","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605142237-ti3rjp0","updated":"20260605142339"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260605142339-zowmln3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142339-zowmln3","updated":"20260605142339"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14．本题考查学生对诗歌的综合理解和赏析能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142339-bej7s3r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142339-bej7s3r","updated":"20260605142339"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D.“表达了真挚的思念之情”错。“与君同醉醒”，意思是与友人一同醉醒，表达闲适自在的心情。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142339-qhqoxbz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142339-qhqoxbz","updated":"20260605142339"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选D。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142339-9lwidim","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142339-9lwidim","updated":"20260605142339"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．本题考查学生评价诗歌中作者的思想情感的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142339-3l81y7m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142339-3l81y7m","updated":"20260605142339"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“看破空花尘世，放轻昨梦浮名”，意思是看破虚幻的世界，放弃过往的无谓名利。体现出作者处世豁达的人生态度，旷达自然，超凡脱俗。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142339-x6cdg61","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142339-x6cdg61","updated":"20260605142339"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“蜡屐登山真率饮，筇杖穿林自在行，身闲心太平”，意思是穿着蜡屐登山真诚率真地饮酒，带上筇杖自在地行走，身体自由，心灵宁静。据此看出作者宁静从容的心境，诠释着作者退居后乐观淡泊的精神追求。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142339-h10mqjy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142339-h10mqjy","updated":"20260605142339"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“苔纸闲题溪上句，菱唱遥闻烟外声”，意思是闲暇之时在溪边题上一首诗，听着远处传来烟霭外采菱人的歌声。作者对官场失望之后徜徉在山水之间，不问世事，抒写闲适情趣力求解脱之道的旷达胸怀。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142237-5q6au8o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142237-5q6au8o","updated":"20260605142207"}}]}